id: 2602
name: Glitter
power: 1
text: |
  If a player has earned a ribbon in the past 7 days but already
  owned it e CAN once (until e earns another ribbon), by
  announcement, earn N+1 coins where N is the number of current
  players that do not own the same ribbon.
history:
- change:
    type: enactment
  date: 2019-11-11
  agent:
    proposal: "8266"
annotations:
- cfjs:
  - id: '3783'
    called: 2019-12-07
  text: >
    A player cannot use this rule to earn coins for a ribbon
    after e has earned another ribbon, regardless of the
    latter's type or whether e had it already.
